Uses of Package
arrayGenerator.generator

  • Packages that use arrayGenerator.generator 
    Package Description
    arrayGenerator.generator
    Defines Array Generators and provides some implementations thereof.
  • Classes in arrayGenerator.generator used by arrayGenerator.generator 
    Class and Description
    ArrayGenerator
    Defines the interface for classes that generate arrays of arbitrary types
    ArrayGeneratorTest
    Provides some basic tests for array generators: Do the generators generate arrays of the correct size? Do the generators throw the expected negative array size exception if asked to generate an array of negative size?
    ScopedArrayGenerator
    A scoped array generator generates arrays in which the generated elements fall within a certain Scope.
    ScopedArrayGeneratorTest
    Implements additional tests, above those defined in ArrayGeneratorTest, to check that: (1) Values in generated arrays are within the specified arrayGenerator.scope (2) All values in the arrayGenerator.scope are generated.
